<dd><p>Create a descriptive topic branch</p></dd>
<dt><a class="co" id="callout_github_CO1-3" href="ch00/co_github_CO1-3"><img src="/book/en/v2/book/06-github/../../callouts/3.png" alt="3"></a></dt>
<dd><p>Make our change to the code</p></dd>
<dt><a class="co" id="callout_github_CO1-4" href="ch00/co_github_CO1-4"><img src="/book/en/v2/book/06-github/../../callouts/4.png" alt="4"></a></dt>
